---
// SEO Results showcase section
---

<section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-900 via-slate-800 to-blue-900 py-20">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">
          SEO That Drives Real Business Results
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">
          My SEO strategies don't just increase rankings—they generate leads, calls, and sales
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-xl text-center border border-slate-700">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold mb-2 text-green-400">347%</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Organic Traffic Increase</div>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            E-commerce client achieved 347% organic traffic growth in 8 months, 
            resulting in $180K additional annual revenue
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-xl text-center border border-slate-700">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold mb-2 text-blue-400">156%</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-white">More Qualified Leads</div>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Construction company doubled their lead generation through 
            local SEO and conversion optimization
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-xl text-center border border-slate-700">
          <div class="text-5xl font-bold mb-2 text-purple-400">89%</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-white">Phone Call Conversions</div>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
            Service business achieved 89% increase in qualified calls 
            from local search optimization
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Why My SEO Gets Results</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="text-green-400 font-mono text-xl mr-4 mt-1">◉</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-green-400 mb-2">Technical Excellence</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
                  Core Web Vitals optimization, mobile-first indexing, and schema markup 
                  for maximum search engine visibility
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-xl mr-4 mt-1">◉</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-blue-400 mb-2">Conversion-Focused Content</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
                  Content that ranks AND converts—targeting high-intent keywords 
                  that drive actual business results
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="text-purple-400 font-mono text-xl mr-4 mt-1">◉</div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-purple-400 mb-2">Local SEO Mastery</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm">
                  Dominate local search results with Google Business Profile optimization, 
                  citation building, and review strategies
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-700">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">SEO Services Include:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-300">
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              Technical SEO audits & fixes
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              Local search optimization
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-400 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              Content strategy & creation
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-400 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              Conversion rate optimization
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-pink-400 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
              Analytics & ROI tracking
            </li>
          </ul>
          
          <div class="mt-8">
            <a 
              href="/services/seo-optimization"
              class="bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors w-full block text-center"
            >
              Learn More About SEO Services
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>